---
import '@fontsource/poppins';
import '@fontsource-variable/work-sans';
import '@fontsource-variable/manrope';
import '../../app/globals.css';

---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Terms and Conditions - Skyfusion</title>
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
          line-height: 1.6;
          margin: 20px;
          max-width: 800px;
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
          color: white;
      }

      h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
          padding-bottom: 10px;
      }

      h2 {
          font-size: 20px;
          margin-top: 20px;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
          margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
          body {
              margin: 10px;
          }

          h1 {
              font-size: 22px;
          }

          h2 {
              font-size: 18px;
          }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
          h1 {
              font-size: 20px;
          }

          h2 {
              font-size: 16px;
          }

          p {
              font-size: 14px;
          }

          .logo {
              width: 80%;
              margin-left: 0;
          }
      }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-to-bl from-indigo-900 to-indigo-700 text-white">
<header>
  <img src="/skyfusion-logo-W.png" alt="SKYFUSION LOGO" class="logo -ml-4 w-3/6"/>
  <h1 class="font-bold">Terms and Conditions</h1>
  <p>Welcome to Skyfusion! These terms and conditions outline the rules and regulations for the use of Skyfusion's website and services.</p>
</header>

<section>
  <h2 class="font-bold">Non-Refundable Policy</h2>
  <p>All fees paid for workshops, training programs, and other services provided by Skyfusion are non-refundable. We understand that unforeseen circumstances may arise, but due to the nature of our services and the preparation involved, refunds cannot be issued once payment has been made. However, we may consider rescheduling your participation in an upcoming workshop or event, subject to availability and mutual agreement.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2 class="font-bold">Payment Terms</h2>
  <p>Payment for workshops and services must be made in full prior to the start date unless otherwise agreed upon in writing by Skyfusion. Failure to make full payment may result in the cancellation of your registration or participation in the workshop.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2 class="font-bold">Cancellation by Skyfusion</h2>
  <p>Skyfusion reserves the right to cancel or reschedule workshops or events due to unforeseen circumstances or low enrollment. In such cases, participants will be notified in advance, and efforts will be made to accommodate rescheduling or provide alternative solutions.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2 class="font-bold">Participant Responsibilities</h2>
  <p>Participants are responsible for ensuring their eligibility for workshops and events, including meeting any prerequisites or technical requirements specified by Skyfusion. Participants are expected to conduct themselves professionally and respect the rights of others throughout their engagement with Skyfusion.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2 class="font-bold">Intellectual Property</h2>
  <p>All content and materials provided by Skyfusion during workshops or through our services are protected by copyright and intellectual property laws. Participants may not reproduce, distribute, or exploit any materials without prior written consent from Skyfusion.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2 class="font-bold">Changes to Terms and Conditions</h2>
  <p>Skyfusion reserves the right to modify these terms and conditions at any time without prior notice. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on this page. It is your responsibility to review these terms periodically for updates.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns about these terms and conditions, please contact us at:</p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> admin@skyfusion.dev</p>
  <p><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="tel:+233206171719">+233206171719</a></p>
</section>
</body>

</html>
